==Japanese==
===Alternative forms===
機 has many {{w|ryakuji}} (handwritten abbreviations), as it is a common character with many strokes (16):
* [[Image:RYAKUJI_ki_01.png|40px]] [[Image:RYAKUJI_ki_02.png|40px]] [[Image:RYAKUJI_ki_03.png|40px]] [[Image:RYAKUJI_ki_04.png|40px]]
The first is a {{w|phono-semantic}} simplification – the ''on'' reading is “ki” (katakana キ), hence the first simplification is 木 + キ (semantic plus simplified phonetic) – compare [[File:Ryakuji GI.png|30px]] for [[議]] and [[File:RYAKUJI ma.png|30px]] for [[魔]]/[[摩]] – while the remaining characters are purely graphical simplifications.

